IMAPAccount mvrozanti@hotmail.com
Host outlook.office365.com
Port 993
User mvrozanti@hotmail.com
AuthMechs XOAUTH2
PassCmd "python3 /home/m/.config/mutt/mutt_oauth2.py --encryption-pipe '' --decryption-pipe '' --provider microsoft --client-id 9e5f94bc-e8a4-4e73-b8be-63364c29d753 --client-secret '' --format token /home/m/.cache/mutt/mvrozanti@hotmail.com.tokens"
TLSType IMAPS
CertificateFile /etc/ssl/certs/ca-certificates.crt
PipelineDepth 50
Timeout 120

IMAPStore mvrozanti@hotmail.com-remote
Account mvrozanti@hotmail.com

MaildirStore mvrozanti@hotmail.com-local
Subfolders Verbatim
Path ~/.local/share/mail/mvrozanti@hotmail.com/
Inbox ~/.local/share/mail/mvrozanti@hotmail.com/INBOX
Flatten .

Channel mvrozanti@hotmail.com
Far :mvrozanti@hotmail.com-remote:
Near :mvrozanti@hotmail.com-local:
Patterns * !"[Gmail]*"
Expunge Both
CopyArrivalDate yes
Sync All
Create Both
SyncState *
MaxMessages 0
ExpireUnread no
